N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 402.3 - Speed limits

State Regulations

No person shall operate any motorized vehicles upon the
lands under the jurisdiction of the Seventh Park Region (Taconic region), in
excess of 25 miles per hour except as otherwise posted. Notes
